validation.validation: An Investment Pool is required for the Gift.

The Gift Classification cannot be set to Spendable, Undetermined or Non-Pooled if there are any approved or in progress transactions (Gift Payouts, Purchases, Sales, Transfers, Adjustments) or if any of the reinvestment fields, income distribution rule data, purchase or reinvestment worktags, or investment pool have been populated.
